metadata.name: WhosBuilding 2.0 #01
metadata.description:
1/1 3840px x 3840px png

WhosBuilding 2.0 #01 is a manually created multi colour 3d art pattern using GeometryNodes and Python.

Together these base building models create a unique art pattern; And this unique piece if of 1 of 49 of these patterns, which contribute to the collection "WhosBuilding 2.0".

The art comes with the original high-resolution .png format document, and the 4K resolution .png format document; And a certificate of authenticity.
